  "description": "Welcome to Casa Panorama, a beautifully positioned 3-bedroom, 4-bathroom apartment in the renowned urbanisation of Señorio de Aloha, offering breathtaking views of the Mediterranean Sea and the iconic La Concha mountain. Set in the very heart of Nueva Andalucía, this home blends exceptional location with a bright, comfortable interior—ideal for both laid-back holidays and bridging the winters.\n\nThe apartment is designed to make the most of its surroundings, with a spacious terrace that frames the panoramic views. Inside, the layout is open and inviting, with modern furnishings, a fully equipped kitchen, and plenty of natural light throughout. The bedrooms offer a peaceful escape, and the main living area opens directly to outdoor seating where sunrises and evening skies become a daily highlight.\n\nSeñorio de Aloha is one of the most established and well-maintained gated communities in the area, celebrated for its lush landscaped gardens, multiple swimming pools, and even a private padel court for residents. Safety and convenience are prioritised here, and the urbanisation’s elevated position means nearly every corner enjoys incredible views.\n\nLocation is key—Casa Panorama is just a short walk from Centro Plaza, home to cafes, restaurants, boutique shops, and one of the area’s best-known markets. Puerto Banús and its sandy beaches are just minutes away on foot, placing designer shopping, beach clubs, and nightlife at your doorstep. With supermarkets and essential amenities nearby, the apartment offers both comfort and practicality for families, couples, or digital nomads.\n\nPlease note that we welcome families and couples only, no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. Should you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and the group that you will be travelling with so we can request this for you.",
